Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>DSE 考生就係垃圾</blockquote>你咪垃圾中嘅垃圾囉</blockquote><br />\ndse雞巧惡牙 巧京京😫"},{"pid":"0e915e9f4183b83a4e0f5d9053ccbe08d587daa7","tid":447094,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>on9 你有證據到佢唔理?你咪照出佢做果part 佢比人屌你咪拎d證據出黎割席<br />\n佢唔係唔理 係唔想理姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以而家決家一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n*定</blockquote><br />\n其實唔洗死 乜撚野分工得好少分 理撚得佢 你考試拎多一兩分都係番度 最緊要緊係玩死d仆街 不過你肯定自己有證據先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee58774c758a782cf54cdda17a58eb2e3fd99d6","tid":447094,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"咁佢真係爆四？"},{"pid":"7511bd8aa6849b055beb80acf83a261081ee9ac7","tid":447094,"uid":126447,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/111154_2b79b7d821e45d28732489ab83535e8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F111154_2b79b7d821e45d28732489ab83535e8a.jpg&h=1556d883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全名:黃智鋒<br />\n電話:6186 4372<br />\n<br />\n呢條撚樣<br />\n同佢傾project又唔係會潛水果隻<br />\n但佢每次都只係坐係度玩電話<br />\n咁我梗係有屌過佢啦<br />\n跟住條撚屌就係example抄D垃圾出黎<br />\n咁係人都知唔可以抄example<br />\n我話完佢 佢竟然仲係覺得自己啱<br />\n咁都算<br />\n咁之後分好曬工<br />\n每一翻屋企一人做一part<br />\n到個個都做好曬<br />\n第二日佢竟然話以為我講笑<br />\n所以我乜都無做<br />\n之後翻去佢係有做嘅<br />\n但又係抄D example<br />\n咁咪即係乜柒都無做<br />\n到之後交咗第一次比lecturer睇<br />\n咁正堂都有D野可以改<br />\n但條撚屌就衝出黎話做咩做到錯曬<br />\n一早同你地講唔係咁做<br />\n但明明佢就乜柒都無做過<br />\n一係就做埋曬D垃圾<br />\n最衰嘅就係佢仲周圍同人唱<br />\n話自己gpa爆四 又話自己上年carry全部project<br />\n我地先係free rider<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係唔想同lecturer投訴<br />\n我地連佢偷懶嘅証據都影低埋<br />\n但個lecturer話佢唔理<br />\n叫我地自己傾好 唔係就扣我地分工嘅分<br />\n有無巴絲可以話比我聽可以點做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁大個人做野都無撚腦 抵撚你死啦樓主<br />\n乜柒都放上黎 on99"},{"pid":"c64c16f2ad684a53034f6447ab77bd3ed4548dea","tid":447094,"uid":28206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁佢真係爆四？</blockquote><br />\n佢好似啱啱好過3"},{"pid":"f68ddd447d5e8a43019c266c5b105e8255e0eca2","tid":447094,"uid":28206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>on9 你有證據到佢唔理?你咪照出佢做果part 佢比人屌你咪拎d證據出黎割席<br />\n佢唔係唔理 係唔想理姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以而家決家一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n*定</blockquote><br />\n其實唔洗死 乜撚野分工得好少分 理撚得佢 你考試拎多一兩分都係番度 最緊要緊係玩死d仆街 不過你肯定自己有證據先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果科無exam<br />\n淨係得project"},{"pid":"33d81dda1dd3d61f25d64d54f954ed3910a84ef4","tid":447094,"uid":2959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"ok 網絡公審"},{"pid":"708b1e72ae4946776e412854c24d728d7f4f66eb","tid":447094,"uid":8733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:39:49.000Z","msg":"乜撚野都要放上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd81f2af11cc0b2b2521f11fdee72a2d73bd42b","tid":447094,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"hog rider<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebb279a28e7c2a9551ee89055be856c0131b04e","tid":447094,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"照咁既勢 如果黃生見到呢個post<br />\n實會post埋樓主個名上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7998c3925a0f712e8d25ed983b4d85b11243707","tid":447094,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike